ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of GORDON DAVID GILLIS of Dartmouth, Nova Scotia, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Nova Scotia, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Linda Yvonne Ivany.
